tabs.title: GoldIntersections
tabs.text:
.create materialized-view with (dimensionTables = dynamic(["SilverCallsigns"])) GoldIntersections on table SilverWeather
{
let preproc_callsigns = () {
SilverCallsigns
| project geojson_linestring, callsign, s2, bronze_timestamp, silver_timestamp
| project-rename linestring_s2 = s2, callsigns_bronze_timestamp=bronze_timestamp, callsigns_silver_timestamp=silver_timestamp
| mv-expand linestring_s2
| extend linestring_s2 = tostring(linestring_s2)
| where isnotempty(linestring_s2) and isnotnull(linestring_s2)
};
SilverWeather
| project isigmetId, polygon,polygon_densified, validTimeFromTimestamp, validTimeToTimestamp, polygon_s2, bronze_timestamp, silver_timestamp
| mv-expand polygon_s2
| extend polygon_s2 = tostring(polygon_s2)
| where isnotempty(polygon_s2) and isnotnull(polygon_s2)
| join kind=inner preproc_callsigns on $left.polygon_s2 == $right.linestring_s2
| project-away linestring_s2, polygon_s2
|extend intersection = geo_intersection_line_with_polygon(geojson_linestring, polygon_densified)
| where not(isnull(intersection))
| where intersection.type != "GeometryCollection"
| project-rename weather_bronze_timestamp=bronze_timestamp, weather_silver_timestamp=silver_timestamp, weather_valid_from=validTimeFromTimestamp, weather_valid_to=validTimeToTimestamp
| extend intersections_gold_timestamp = now()
| project callsign, isigmetId, weather_bronze_timestamp, weather_silver_timestamp,weather_valid_from, weather_valid_to, callsigns_bronze_timestamp, callsigns_silver_timestamp,intersections_gold_timestamp,geojson_linestring,polygon_densified,intersection
| summarize arg_max(weather_bronze_timestamp, *) by isigmetId, callsign
}

tabs.title: Update SilverAlarms
tabs.text:
.create-or-alter function with (docstring = "Looking up current intersections in GoldIntersections this creates alarm if based on current position weather hazard will be approximately reached.", folder = "UpdatePolicy")
GetAlarms()
{
SilverOpenskynet
| project icao24, longitude, latitude, callsign, bronze_timestamp, silver_timestamp
| project-rename openskynet_bronze_timestamp=bronze_timestamp, openskynet_silver_timestamp=silver_timestamp
| join kind=inner GoldIntersections on callsign
| project-away callsign1
| extend linestring_current_dest = bag_pack("type", "Linestring", "coordinates", pack_array(pack_array(longitude, latitude), geojson_linestring.coordinates[-1]))
| extend current_hazard_intersects = geo_intersects_line_with_polygon(linestring_current_dest, polygon_densified)
| where current_hazard_intersects
| extend intersection_coordinate_longitude_1 = toreal(intersection.coordinates[-1][0]) 
| extend intersection_coordinate_latitude_1 = toreal(intersection.coordinates[-1][1])
| extend intersection_coordinate_longitude_2 = toreal(intersection.coordinates[0][0]) 
| extend intersection_coordinate_latitude_2 = toreal(intersection.coordinates[0][1])
| extend remaining_distance_1 = geo_distance_2points(intersection_coordinate_longitude_1, intersection_coordinate_latitude_1, longitude, latitude)
| extend remaining_time_1 = toint(remaining_distance_1/235)  //average commercial plane speed
| extend remaining_distance_2 = geo_distance_2points(intersection_coordinate_longitude_2, intersection_coordinate_latitude_2, longitude, latitude)
| extend remaining_time_2 = toint(remaining_distance_2/235)  //average commercial plane speed
| where weather_valid_to > datetime_add('second', remaining_time_1, now()) or weather_valid_from > datetime_add('second', remaining_time_2, now())
| extend alarm_silver_timestamp = now()
| project     icao24 , callsign, isigmetId, openskynet_bronze_timestamp,openskynet_silver_timestamp,weather_bronze_timestamp,weather_silver_timestamp, callsigns_bronze_timestamp, callsigns_silver_timestamp, intersections_gold_timestamp, alarm_silver_timestamp
| summarize arg_max(openskynet_bronze_timestamp, openskynet_silver_timestamp,weather_bronze_timestamp,weather_silver_timestamp, callsigns_bronze_timestamp, callsigns_silver_timestamp, intersections_gold_timestamp, alarm_silver_timestamp) by icao24, callsign, isigmetId
}

{
SilverAlarms
| extend alarm_gold_timestamp = now()
| extend id = strcat(icao24,callsign, isigmetId)
| summarize arg_min(alarm_silver_timestamp, *) by icao24, callsign, isigmetId
}
